nome d'arte e marchio registrato Mistura

I'm the holder of the application for trademark number MI2004CC000840filed  
on January 30, 2004 for the trade name “Mistura Pura”, registered for a  
number of product categories, inclusive of category n. 25 (clothing,  
garments and shoes), category n. 35 (advertising and marketing and business  
management) as well as category 41 (entertainment, sporting and cultural  
events). From 2007 January the trade name "Mistura Pura" number is  
n.1080215.
